name: ruby-openai-pinecone
description: A Ruby gem for semantic search using Pinecone and OpenAI API. This gem provides out-of-the-box functionality for generating vectors using the OpenAI API's text-embedding-ada-002 model and uploading them to Pinecone for efficient semantic search. description: SVG:::Graph is a pure Ruby library for generating charts, which are a type of graph where the values of one axis are not scalar. This isn't surprising, because SVG::Graph started as a loose port of SVG::TT::Graph.
